reviewText: This live DVD is awesome. For all the true fans, this is definitely a must have! It feels as if you're actually there watching them live in concert. They all look and sound great. It's just a perfect way to say goodbye!

An incredible DVD.  Once again RBD shows why they became the musical phenomenon, that captivated the hearts of millions all around the world.  This is a must have DVD for all RBD fans and those who love good music.
